        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC now includes a 32-Bit 80386 Native mode executable"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "compatible with OS/2 Version 2.0+.  Capable of executing from both"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "a Window and an OS/2 fullscreen, the 32-Bit OS/2 version runs"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "faster than its predecessor, and can load larger files."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "As in previous versions, SPF/PC for DOS is a 32-Bit native"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "executable as well."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For further details see:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC User Guide and Reference,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC Files ..................... Page 2-12"
      }
    ]
  },
